and aspirations suddenly exploding, on being released from the realm of dreams
into the realm of the real and the possible. In changing their environment
people themselves were changed. Those who had never dared say anything suddenly
felt their thoughts to be the most important thing in the world—and said so. The
shy became communicative. The helpless and isolated suddenly discovered that
